caption.text:
More in caption⬇️

1. Get Leads, Not Views✏️

Remember what you’re making content for. 

You’re trying to attract customers.

Would you rather have 1,000,000 randomers watch your content…

or 20,000 specifically targetted viewers who are your perfect target audience?

Think about it.

2. Will you get clients from posting content?💸

Be realistic.

You can’t expect people to reach out to you after posting 2/3 reels offering you a $2k/mo retainer.

But what you can do to increase your chances is:

1.) Refine your offer, dial in your skillet.

2.) Target your messaging at your ideal target avatar.

3.) Focus of optimising your bottom of funnel (lead magnets, long form content, call to actions, DM setting etc.)

I was lucky enough to get my first few clients after 20 posts at 150 followers, showcase your skills and see what happens:)

3. JUST POST📲

The biggest issue that people face when ‘creating’ is ANALYSIS PARALYSIS.

Do not spend all you time plotting and ‘coming up with plans’ to create.

Take action.

Your first few reels will be sh*t.

But your 1000th might be half decent;)

Get after it.

Comment ‘Creator’ and I’ll send across my newsletter that has a bunch more value in it:)

This past week has been insane⬇️

I’ve been posting on this account for 7 weeks now.

In the first week I think I gained 300 followers😂

There’s so much more to come…

Excited for this month, drop me a follow of you haven’t already😎
